Beyond Nails, Beyond Beautiful!

With years of expertise in the nail industry, at julie Nails in Knoxville, TN 37919, we believes that every visit should be a delightful experience. We strive to create an environment where you can relax, unwind, and leave feeling more beautiful than ever.

Nail Buffet: Crafting Your Perfect Look!
🗸 Hundreds of colors that are frequently updated.
🗸 Diverse techniques of SNS/Dipping Powder, Acrylic, Gel color,…
🗸 Trendy designs like Pink & White/French, Ombre, holograph/foil/chrome, and more.
🗸 Shapes: coffin, square, stiletto, round, oval, almond, etc.

Deluxe Mani/Pedi Packages: Pamper from Tip to Toe!
• Various packages tailored to your desires and available time.
• Complete care with high-quality products from trusted suppliers.

Grade-A Sanitation: Your Safety is Our Priority!
All tools are sterilized, and single-use items are discarded after each customer. Our space is sanitized daily at our nail salon Kingston Pike to ensure a hygienic environment for every visit.

We are more than just a nail salon – we are a place where creativity meets care, and every detail is crafted to make you feel special. Looking for the best nail salon near me that accept walk-ins? Come visit julie Nails at 5445, 9 Atlanta Hwy Suite H, Alpharetta, GA, United States, Georgia and let us turn your beauty dreams into reality!
